definitions.definition: A dense clump of grass or vegetation ; a tussock .
A cushion used primarily in churches for kneeling on while praying .
A thick cushion used as a seat ; an ottoman or pouffe .

main_definition: A dense clump of grass or vegetation ; a tussock . [from 10th c.]
secondary_definitions: A cushion used primarily in churches for kneeling on while praying . [from 16th c.]
A thick cushion used as a seat ; an ottoman or pouffe .
